column5: will these work for carrrps too?
Thanks GCD. I could use a new recipe or to for trout.

some good looking recipes there coach..with some great rainbow action awaiting a month or so from now, that might come in handy for scoring extra brownie points with the wife  , if she likes it, maybe she will make me go fishing more too!!!
Some nice recipes there GCD thanks I will have to convert them to PDF for future reference just in case of any pending trout harvesting situations become reality.
Thanks for the info....now, off to the blue zone!
